			<h3 class="h2 mt-5 mb-2">
				Introduction
			</h3>
			<p class="fw-normal">Welcome to Tasty Drink Bar & Shop! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled responsibly. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the steps we take to safeguard your information.</p>

